    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管美国反对，泽伦斯基仍誓言用无人机袭击俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-vows-more-strikes-on-russia-despite-us-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，尽管美国对其行动不满意，乌克兰仍将继续瞄准俄罗斯炼油设施。他警告说，如果没有盟友提供更多军事援助，基辅军队可能被迫“逐步”撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-vows-more-strikes-on-russia-despite-us-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 10:56:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚旅游业收入跃升 32%，超过疫情前水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/kenya-tourism-earnings-jump-32-to-surpass-pre-pandemic-level</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年，肯尼亚的旅游业收入猛增 32%，达到 3525 亿先令（27 亿美元），因为入境人数的增加推动收入达到自 Covid-19 大流行爆发以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-30/kenya-tourism-earnings-jump-32-to-surpass-pre-pandemic-level</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 10:35:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
